  "ai_packaging_info": "Great question! 📦 We use export-grade packaging:\n\n🍌 Bananas → Corrugated boxes with poly liners\n🥥 Coconuts → Shrink-wrapped pallets & jute bags\n🥬 Vegetables → Ventilated crates & perforated poly bags\n\nAll packaging meets ISPM-15 standards. ✨",
